text: Majur (, ) is a village located in the municipality of Šabac, Serbia. The village has a Serb ethnic majority and its population numbered 7,031 inhabitants as of 2011 census. ==See also== * List of places in Serbia * Mačva ==References== ==External links== Category:Mačva Category:Populated places in Mačva District
title: Majur (Šabac)
